s-meet-new-york-2024-09-23/</guid></item><item><title>受伤的雷巴基娜缺席北京和武汉，但在 WTA 总决赛前复眼</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/injured-rybakina-skips-beijing-wuhan-eyes-return-before-wta-finals-2024-09-23/</link><description>前温布尔登冠军埃琳娜·雷巴基娜表示，由于背部问题，她已经退出了北京和武汉的比赛，但她的目标是在 11 月份在利雅得举行的 WTA 巡回赛赛季收官赛之前重返赛场。</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Sep 2024 03:52:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/injured-rybakina-skips-beijing-wuhan-eyes-return-before-wta-finals-2024-09-23/</guid></item><item><title>据彭博社报道，花旗集团在中国的扩张受到美国监管机构的阻碍</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/citigroups-china-expansion-plan-put-hold-by-us-regulators-bloomberg-news-reports-2024-09-23/</link><description>据彭博社周日报道，在美联储对其数据管理和风险控制进行处罚后，花旗集团在中国的扩张计划遇到了美国监管机构的障碍。</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Sep 2024 00:57:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/citigroups-china-expansion-plan-put-hold-by-us-regulators-bloomberg-news-reports-2024-09-23/</guid></item><item><title>股市和华尔街期货公司即将出台更多宽松政策</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-09-23/</link><description>周一，全球股市在亚洲走强，此前人们普遍预计央行会议将再进行两次降息，而美国关键通胀数据也将为进一步宽松政策打开绿灯。</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Sep 2024 00:35:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-09-23/</guid></item><item><title>调查显示约40%的地区、城市和企业缺乏减排目标</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/climate-energy/some-40-regions-cities-companies-lack-emissions-cut-targets-survey-says-2024-09-22/</link><description>根据周一发布的年度“盘点”，衡量全球应对灾难性气候变化的进展情况，超过 40% 的主要企业、城市和地区仍未设定任何减少温室气体排放的目标。</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2024 23:07:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/climate-energy/some-40-regions-cities-companies-lack-emissions-cut-targets-survey-says-2024-09-22/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：美联储肾上腺素持续飙升，央行惯性可能拖累</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-09-22/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2024 21:49:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-09-22/</guid></item><item><title>香港首位跨性别创作歌手通过音乐寻求声音</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kongs-first-transgender-singer-songwriter-seeks-voice-through-music-2024-09-22/</link><description>香港第一位备受瞩目的变性歌手兼词曲作者吴晓明 (Xavian Wu) 试图利用周日举行的香港一年一度的 LGBTQ 粉红点嘉年华，通过音乐分享他的故事。</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2024 08:09:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kongs-first-transgender-singer-songwriter-seeks-voice-through-music-2024-09-22/</guid></item><item><title>独家：美国提议禁止联网汽车中的中国软件、硬件</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/us-propose-barring-chinese-software-hardware-connected-vehicles-sources-say-2024-09-21/</link><description>美国政府对中国公司收集数据的行为表示严重关切。</description><pubDate>Sat, 21 Sep 2024 21:43:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/us-propose-barring-chinese-software-hardware-connected-vehicles-sources-say-2024-09-21/</guid></item><item><title>拜登和日本首相岸田讨论对南海的共同担忧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/japan/biden-japans-kishida-discuss-shared-concerns-over-south-china-sea-2024-09-21/</link><description>领导人重申致力于推进和保护人工智能和半导体技术。</description><pubDate>Sat, 21 Sep 2024 17:24:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/japan/biden-japans-kishida-discuss-shared-concerns-over-south-china-sea-2024-09-21/</guid></item><item><title>意大利艺术展开幕式上男子砸碎艾未未雕塑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/man-smashes-ai-weiwei-sculpture-italy-art-show-opening-2024-09-21/</link><description>展览发言人表示，周五，在意大利博洛尼亚法瓦宫举办的中国艺术家和活动家艾未未的展览开幕式上，一名男子打碎了他的雕塑。</description><pubDate>Sat, 21 Sep 2024 15:08:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/man-smashes-ai-weiwei-sculpture-italy-art-show-opening-2024-09-21/</guid></item><item><title>台湾发生5.3级地震，目前尚无受损报告</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-rattled-by-53-magnitude-quake-no-immediate-reports-damage-2024-09-21/</link><description>台湾气象部门表示，周六，台湾人口稀少的东海岸花莲县发生了 5.3 级地震，目前尚未收到受损情况报告。</description><pubDate>Sat, 21 Sep 2024 11:11:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-rattled-by-53-magnitude-quake-no-immediate-reports-damage-2024-09-21/</guid></item><item><title>机构报告称，俄罗斯和中国开始在日本海举行海军演习</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/russia-china-start-naval-exercises-sea-japan-agencies-report-2024-09-21/</link><description>俄罗斯新闻机构援引俄罗斯太平洋舰队的消息称，俄罗斯和中国周六开始在日本海举行海军演习。</description><pubDate>Sat, 21 Sep 2024 09:23:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/russia-china-start-naval-exercises-sea-japan-agencies-report-2024-09-21/</guid></item></channel></rss>